rows.label: tlk43300046_07_msg0001
rows.name:
I've finally mastered the
Roast Meat Tagliata!

rows.label: tlk43300046_07_msg0002
rows.name:
I even got the head cook's
seal of approval.

rows.label: tlk43300046_07_msg0003
rows.name:
I knew I was on to something using my
axe instead of the regular carving knife.
And the plates I used were good, too.

rows.label: tlk43300046_07_msg0004
rows.name:
Anyway, I'm one step closer to the day
when I will finally be able to cook for
the esteemed Queen Lagert!

rows.label: tlk43300046_07_msg0005
rows.name:
This is partly thanks to you, so
why don't I teach you a recipe
as a sign of my gratitude.
